<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - 捉妖工具</title>
    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-1.10.2.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/cookie.min.js"></script>

    <script src="~/Content/bootstrap/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <link href="~/Content/bootstrap/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
    <script src="~/js/clipboard.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-default">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="navbar-header">
                    <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">捉妖工具</a>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="dropdown" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">已知妖灵</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="dropdown" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Setting">全局设置</a>
                        </li>

                    </ul>
                    <div class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </nav>

    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <img class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6" src="~/image/weixinsearch.png" />
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                微信小程序"捉妖工具"的网页版，若要在移动设备上使用，请在微信上搜索并使用小程序版<br /><br />
                首次使用请先进入全局设置进行配置，每款软件的坐标系和格式都不同<br /><br />
                如有问题请加QQ群：7672057
            </div>
        </div>
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="border-top footer text-muted">
        <div class="container">
            &copy; 2019 - 捉妖工具
        </div>
    </footer>



    @RenderSection("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
